    {
        "id": "9e0a6ed18a5ea36d",
        "type": "comment",
        "z": "ab1b0ea518202bba",
        "name": "ReadMe",
        "info": "-->payload from producer\n\n-->switch for motion detected or clear\n\n## If detected:\n\n# function 1 determines activity level (function 5 is clone of 1 with different topic)\n\n-->payload is sent to smartbin/bin-01/usage/nodered\n(can be checked from terminal)\n\n-->payload is sent to smartbin/bin-01/alerts\n(straight to home assistant)\n\n-->also to gauge and text for ui\n(can be checked in \"http://<raspberry-ip>:1881/dashboard)\n-->function 4 formats payload for ui\n\n-->Write events in file one per bin, func 8 dynamicly changes filename\n\n# -->swich for high \n\n-->POST in API\n-->format message in function 3 and publish notification in dsahboard\n\n\n",
        "x": 160,
        "y": 260,
        "wires": []
